{"tid":1708522,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"檢討：點解塞極都塞唔到？點解咁多手足被捕？","createTime":"2019-11-11T15:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T15:42:13.000Z","uid":198258,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"52a6f3ad7562451c0b3f6ad49b289f3568d73c48","tid":1708522,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:13:45.000Z","msg":"要聚一大班人先開始起rb，而且rb極易比人清走。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣比黑警知道曬你係邊到做野，佢梗係識得放一堆鬼啦。<br />\n<br />\n請放棄人多就安全嘅諗法，落手嘅轉為小組行動四圍去，唔好再同和理非痴埋一齊。<br />\nRB快快手起完就走。<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣起rb先又快又唔易清？<br />\n拋磚：<br />\n事先準備好大量膠釘/老鼠膠等快乾膠，將雜物痴係地。<br />\n膠釘唔好慢慢唧，直接折開黎用。<br />\n<br />\n靠大家再諗下"},{"pid":"77c4c7bb2bf70a869b64bfffe83196a1d6ca50cd","tid":1708522,"uid":10630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pVpV1zs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpVpV1zs.png&h=1f014782&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a400caad40cb1326656f5af25ac73aa58567b8a","tid":1708522,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:14:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b622b3f183e91a10909114c00cbe92c0cbe17e8","tid":1708522,"uid":320934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到但support"},{"pid":"647fa5699d00dc6ce8ef759612ec25afaec16b37","tid":1708522,"uid":170014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:16:01.000Z","msg":"太多港豬同藍絲廢老 set 完rb 之後佢哋落手落腳清"},{"pid":"7753a50a0f0e1cffdc29c769c49244ad3b042d00","tid":1708522,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:16:28.000Z","msg":"小隊內， 一定要有一個平民裝長時間mon tg, HKmap live 做哨"},{"pid":"3a48d39b65572f46127f6d332571e4293e98f142","tid":1708522,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T15:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTU68fz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTU68fz.